---
title: Buttery Sesame Shrimp Noodles with Teriyaki-Sauced Veggies
description: The starting lineup of this recipe features juicy roasted shrimp that pop with the flavour of toasted sesame. Served atop saucy noodles, tender-crisp veggies make for a sumptuous dinner for the whole family.

